We support public & active transport, & if we are to increase patronage into the CBD we need to make it desirable, compelling, safe, easy. 26% of respondents have changed where they walk as a result of e-mobility parking /rider behaviour. That impacts business. 50% said that footpaths have cracks, trip hazards, 48% said f‚Äôpaths were too narrow for üõ¥ parking. 39% experienced a safety issue on footpaths (trip/ hit)
